      </p>
      <span class="text-white">
        Powered by
        <a
          href="https://rightruddermarketing.com/"
          target="_blank"
          class="text-bold hover:underline hover:text-white/70"
        >
          More Right Rudder</a
        >
      </span>
      <div class="flex items-center mt-4 space-x-4 sm:mt-0">
        <a
